New on mobile: Price charts

Our goal with Farcaster is to work with ecosystems where people are building interesting things onchain.

Make it easy for Farcaster users to try them out.

Make it easy for Farcaster builders to build new things.

People shouldn't have to think about extensions, onramps, chains, bridging, gas, etc. 

Instead, it should be as easy as seeing an interesting link in a feed and clicking on it.

If you could have us add / improve one thing in wallet, what would it be?

Recent additions
1. Solana, Celo and Monad support
2. Faster / background swaps
3. Price charts on token pages

What else?
